      public Level(int id, int scoreToNextLevel)
      Creats the object Level
      pre: the array level must be created
      post: Initializes the variables in this object and creates the enemy and treasure arrays.
      Parameters:
      id - Is the unique id of the new player.
      scoreToNextLevel - is the number of points a player must reach to advance level.
      enemies - is the array containing the levels of the game.
      treasures - is the array containing the treasures of the game.
